result.name: Qinghai Beef Noodles

reviews.text:
I like their deep fried chicken noodles!! 
$48 Lunch set comes with soft drink
The texture of the noodle is totally wrong. Really don’t know why this place is so popular.
Nice soup without MSG😍
Good service, very tasty food and decent prices.

Was in the area and looked for lunch/tea.  Had thought to go Western in this same street but decided to give hot noodles a try since the weather was beginning to get cooler.  Great value for the quality of food, lunch set cost ~50 includes a drink, Coke zero also available.  I got the beef thick noodles, beef taste great, not too much fat, love the noodles, and the soup base is pretty good.  FYI, they do start turning customers aways 10 mins to 3pm cuz they close between 3pm to 6pm.

result.name: 青藏牛肉麵

reviews.text: 麵條咀勁十足😋

I like their deep fried chicken noodles!! 
$48 Lunch set comes with soft drink
美味又有很多選擇，特別羊肉，牛肉串燒很好吃！
平日食lunch都會去，湯底好香好好味，跟餐有小食送，幾有心做要支持本地小店！
友人昨晚試了幾道菜，羊肉串、羊架、牛肉麵、茄子和青瓜。羊架能保持羊嘅鮮味和啖啖肉汁，超好味👍！反之，青瓜過鹹，隔離的客人都吃不消！👎
